reviewText: i bought this for the new birth.  of course there are other great performances on here.  the new birth performs only one song - but this lineup still includes bobby downs and ann bogan.  if you are a fan - then this is to be cherished, they perform the song "it's impossible".  there is a very short clip on youtube - you get the whole performance here.  and like i said - if you are a fan - this is gold.
Great show with excellent interviews. You have to wonder why it was cancelled after one year. Hmmmm!!!!
This is a classic collection of well-done interviews of some of America's brightest (and often forgotten) stars.
